{"tid":2281432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾翰林案被指涉協助罪犯 陸海天獲保釋候查","createTime":"2020-11-11T07:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T08:51:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4c80c10c652d1ee49e926b3432838641d84386","tid":2281432,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"已解散的學生動源前召集人鍾翰林，上月底前往美國駐港總領事館尋求政治庇護前，在附近被國安處警員拘捕，扣查40小時後，警方以違反國安法再拘捕他；同日學生動源前成員何忻諾及陳渭賢亦被捕。警方國安處經進一步調查後，本月9日在元朗區拘捕前學生動源成員陸海天，涉嫌協助罪犯。直至昨晚，陸海天已獲准保釋候查，下月中再向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201111/MKXGF3PU6RGGJBEHQHT2NY6DFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201111%2FMKXGF3PU6RGGJBEHQHT2NY6DFY%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=0fbcbafe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201111%2FMKXGF3PU6RGGJBEHQHT2NY6DFY%2F&h=58c18fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201111/MKXGF3PU6RGGJBEHQHT2NY6DFY/</a>"},{"pid":"0c36165618d48ea5ab5f4aee1fec88c51ece5254","tid":2281432,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8c6c81058760c44b4ba6846004114f37b9c556","tid":2281432,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:44:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e017d4f02b2b8ef93e5b0138ca50f9d2e32fb78","tid":2281432,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill